Class AStar

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.smcm.ai.search.Search
      • edu.smcm.ai.search.UniformCostSearch

  • public class AStar
extends UniformCostSearch
    An A* search is a Uniform Cost Search where the frontier queue is replaced by a frontier queue sorted with a heuristic. See Russell and Norvig, Artificial Intelligence: A Modern Approach, Third Edition, p. 93.
